ZH: 我昨天去医院检查，发现我得了一种罕见的疾病。
EN: I went to the hospital yesterday for a check-up and found out that I have a rare illness.

ZH: 我的朋友正在康复中，他在和一种顽固的疾病作斗争。
EN: My friend is in the process of recovery, he is battling with a stubborn disease.

ZH: 疾病的传播可以通过接触感染或者空气传播。
EN: The spread of diseases can occur through direct contact or airborne transmission.

ZH: 女儿得了一种常见的儿童疾病，但是现在正在慢慢康复。
EN: My daughter caught a common childhood illness, but she is slowly recovering now.

ZH: 小猫狗在拥抱和亲吻时传播的疾病是一种常见的传染病。
EN: The diseases spread through hugging and kissing cats and dogs are common infectious diseases.

ZH: 我们必须加强卫生习惯以避免罹患某些疾病。
EN: We must improve our hygiene habits to avoid contracting certain diseases.

ZH: 这种疾病在年轻人中有高发病率。
EN: This disease has a high incidence rate among young people.

ZH: 这种疾病可以治疗，但是没有特效药物。
EN: This disease is treatable, but there is no specific medication for it.

ZH: 他一直忙于研究这种疾病的治疗方法。
EN: He has been busy researching treatment methods for this disease.

ZH: 预防措施可以减少疾病的传播。
EN: Preventive measures can reduce the spread of diseases.

ZH: 老年人更容易受到某些慢性疾病的影响。
EN: Elderly people are more susceptible to certain chronic diseases.

ZH: 高血压是一种常见的疾病，但是可以通过药物和健康生活方式控制。
EN: Hypertension is a common disease, but it can be controlled with medication and a healthy lifestyle.

ZH: 这种疾病需要定期检查以及长期的治疗。
EN: This disease requires regular check-ups and long-term treatment.

ZH: 某些疾病的症状可能需要进行进一步的诊断和检查。
EN: Symptoms of certain diseases may require further diagnosis and examination.

ZH: 疫苗是预防某些传染病的最有效方法之一。
EN: Vaccination is one of the most effective methods to prevent certain infectious diseases.

ZH: 长时间的压力可能导致许多疾病的发生。
EN: Prolonged stress can contribute to the occurrence of many diseases.

ZH: 疾病的早期检测和治疗可以提供更好的治愈率。
EN: Early detection and treatment of diseases can provide a better chance of recovery.

ZH: 世界卫生组织正在致力于控制和消灭一些致命的传染疾病。
EN: The World Health Organization is committed to controlling and eradicating some deadly infectious diseases.

ZH: 我们需要关注健康教育，提高普通人对疾病的认识。
EN: We need to focus on health education and raise public awareness of diseases.

ZH: 为了预防疾病的传播，我们需要采取有效的个人卫生措施。
EN: To prevent the spread of diseases, we need to take effective personal hygiene measures.
